modName: Realistic Skyrim V3 - ENB Alternative No FPS Hit
summary: A Realistic Skyrim - Better lighting, shadows. Cleaner, cripser look.
descriptionHtml:
****************INTRODUCTION*****************

Realistic Skyrim V3 is a custom FXAA Injector that turns Skyrim from a \"cartoony\" look to a \"realistic\" look.

Check the screens for the differences of some varied scenes.

*Minimal performance drop unlike ENB. Does not affect my FPS at all, if you have an older machine and/or poor graphics card there is a chance your frames may drop by ~4,5FPS

* Change your brightness in-game once you activate the mod to something you like. Everyone has a different monitor and some people will need to raise the brightness for best results.

* It does not have ENB included.

* You do not need to download anything else - no ENB, no FXAA, all files required are included in the download.

* If you already have an ENB, FXAA or other injector installed - I would remove them, then install this mod or you may have issues.
******************************************************





****************INSTALLATION*****************

1. Copy all files to your \"Skyrim\" folder where \"TESV.exe\" is located.   NOT the Data folder. 

2. Press \"Pause/Break\" in game to toggle on and off.

******************************************************




****************CREDIT*****************
These settings are based on \"Himmelsrand Custom Shader Suite\" by Hunin. 
You can find his original mod here http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=240


Credit to some_dude and others for the original FXAA Injector for Skyrim.
******************************************************
author: MrCooper
